Set Choice `RequestChoice "Gloom 3 Zombie Edition Extras Menu By Gareth Murfin" "What rejects would you like to look at?" "Sounds please!" "Graphics please!" "Emm none Ive changed my mind.."`
If Val $Choice EQ 2  
 Run >nil: gfx/VT DF GFX/
EndIf
If Val $Choice EQ 1
 Run >nil: sfx/Play16 path sfx/ Multiple
EndIf
If Val $Choice EQ 0
 RequestChoice "" "Hey the rejects are funny!" "Ok, Ill look at them later!" > NIL:
EndIf
